15namespace webrtc {
16
17rtc::scoped_refptr<VideoFrameBuffer> ObjCToNativeVideoFrameBuffer(
18 id<RTCVideoFrameBuffer> objc_video_frame_buffer) {
19 return new rtc::RefCountedObject<ObjCFrameBuffer>(objc_video_frame_buffer);
20}
21
22id<RTCVideoFrameBuffer> NativeToObjCVideoFrameBuffer(
23 const rtc::scoped_refptr<VideoFrameBuffer> &buffer) {
24 return ToObjCVideoFrameBuffer(buffer);
25}

27} // namespace webrtc
